title: High.Definition.Music.Videos
description:
This collection of HD videos (mostly from the Jools Holland program) has been building over some time now. As of late, I've been converting many of my 1080p videos to 720p since A) they look identical and B) I can't watch 1080p videos if my computer is in a state any more active than "idle".

So there are plenty duplications in here of the same video in both 1080p and 720p formats. Although there are some that are only in 1080p and others that are only in 720p format (those are the ones I never converted either way).

Anyway, there's a lot to choose from here and I think, for the most part, this music is what I would call "quality" music. There's even some classical (Beethoven) in there if you like to listen to that.

The directory structure is broken down into two sub-folders: "720p" and "1080p". So it should be easy to spot what the differences are and you can pick and choose from either set Ã¢â‚¬Â¦ or just take them all and re-seed them!
